reviewText: very nice product, however the dvd cant play in america :l

I didn't really care much about the content of the DVD, so if you want to know how the show is, well I don't know. However, the figma is top knotch. While not as articulated as a lot of figures, it is really good looking, especially sexy with big breasts, a huge ass with the swimsuit barely covering her ass-cheeks and having a nice plumber-crack, and also the most Moe-looking face you can imagine. If you want proof of a figma being a guilty pleasure, than Sonico has it all.

- the beautiful & sexy sonico is made into an amazing figure by FIGMA .

- this is a special edition of her in blkini !

- she is very articulated , and comes with a good amount of accessories .

- If you love Super Sonico or just a figma collector you'll love it !
